summary:
The Sinister Blade
League Of Legends Inspired Katarina
descriptionHtml:
[size=5]Hello :)
[size=4]this is a simple present for Katarina if you want your character to look like her. She is League of Legends inspired^^[/size]

For her armor I used the TERA armor collection
[size=4]
To make her look exactly like this you will have to install a couple of mods im sorry^^
hope you enojoy :D[/size][/size]
[size=5]Mods ESSENTIAL:[/size]

[list][*][size=4]SKSE[/size][/*]
[*][size=3]Racemenu[/size][/*]
[*][size=3]RaceComnpability with Fixes[/size][/*]

[size=3]
[u]How To Install:[/u]
The Installation Is very easy and should not take much time.
[i]1st[/i]
Go to C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\SteamApps\common\Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets
[i]2nd[/i]
If you haven't saved any Character Presents yet, this folder may be empty, but just put my file [i]0.slot[/i] in there, this contains Moniques Present. [b]Overwrite if asked.[/b]
[i]3rd[/i]
Then open your game and go into the RaceMenu (open console by ^ and type in
showracemenu, enter), there at the bottom you should be able to see Load
Present (F5). Press that and your character willÂ  load up. It should
look like mine, if not I'm sorry.

I made thsi mod for fun and i hope you enjoy :)
- Fiona[/size]
